<ul><li> When Kazumi is <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CameraFiend" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CameraFiend">taking pictures of everyone at the end of the trip to Kyoto</a>, she takes a picture of several of her classmates in the hot springs, including Mana Tatsumiya. She was hiding a gun under a bucket and is seconds away from shooting Kazumi.
